5-19:152\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\">Build interactive, responsive, and high-performance user interfaces using React.js (including Hooks, Context API, and Redux for state management).</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"20:5-20:107\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\">Ensure cross-browser compatibility <span class=\"citation-0\">and optimize applications for maximum speed and scalability.</span></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"21:5-21:105\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><span class=\"citation-0 citation-end-0\">Collaborate with UI/UX designers to translate wireframes and mockups<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></span> into high-quality code.<!----><span class=\"button-container hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"> &nbsp; <button class=\"mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger button image-fade-on hide-from-message-actions\" aria-label=\"Learn More\" aria-controls=\"sources\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-describedby=\"cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-32\"></button><!----></span><!----></span>\r\n<div class=\"container ng-tns-c1495087998-55 hide\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><!----></span>\r\n<div class=\"carousel-container ng-tns-c1495087998-55\">\r\n<div class=\"carousel-content ng-tns-c1495087998-55\">\r\n<div class=\"sources-carousel-source ng-tns-c1495087998-55 hide ng-star-inserted\" data-test-id=\"sources-carousel-source\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><!----></span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><!----><!----></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><!----></span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"22:1-25:113\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Backend Development:</strong></span>\r\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"23:5-25:113\">\r\n<li style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"23:5-23:98\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\">Design and implement robust, scalable, and secure RESTful APIs using Node.js and Express.js.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"24:5-24:58\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\">Integrate third-party services and APIs as required.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"25:5-25:113\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\">Develop and manage database schemas and queries for MongoDB, ensuring efficient data storage and retrieval.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"26:1-26:136\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Database Management:</strong> Work with MongoDB to design and optimize database models, write efficient queries, and manage data migration.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"27:1-27:179\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Code Quality &amp; Testing:</strong> Write clean, well-documented, and reusable code. Conduct unit, integration, and end-to-end testing to ensure application quality and reliability.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"28:1-28:147\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Participate in agile development methodologies (Scrum/Kanban), including daily stand-ups, sprint planning, and retrospectives.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"29:1-29:149\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Problem Solving:</strong> Troubleshoot and debug applications, identify bottlenecks, and implement solutions to improve performance and user experience.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"30:1-30:122\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Deployment &amp; Maintenance:</strong> Assist with deployment processes, monitoring, and ongoing maintenance of applications.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 2; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\" data-sourcepos=\"31:1-32:0\"><span style=\"font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino, serif;\"><strong>Stay Updated:</strong> Keep abreast of new technologies and best practices in full-stack development, particularly within the MERN ecosystem.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','JavaScript,React,Angular,Vue.js,Node.js','Full Time','₹20L-₹30L','Senior','3-5 Years','Male','Web Development','Bachelor\'s Degree','2025-06-30','active','2025-05-10 21:27:10','2025-05-10 21:27:10');
