it, integration, and end-to-end testing to ensure application quality and reliability.\r\nCollaboration: Participate in agile development methodologies (Scrum/Kanban), including daily stand-ups, sprint planning, and retrospectives.\r\n','Java,Python,JavaScript,Node.js,NoSQL,MongoDB,Machine Learning,AI','Full Time','₹10L-₹15L','Senior','7-10 Years','Male','EdTech','Bachelor\'s Degree','2025-07-30','active','2025-05-10 20:26:33','2025-05-10 20:26:33');
